</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/62249448-mohammed-motiwala">Mohammed Motiwala</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
This answer contains spoilers…
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    The shots that Sartaj hears could mean that the Guru is dead. However there is little reason for the Black Cats to shoot a man on a wheelchair, even i<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    The shots that Sartaj hears could mean that the Guru is dead. However there is little reason for the Black Cats to shoot a man on a wheelchair, even in the midst of a gun battle. Considering the man that the Guru was i doubt he would take a gun to save himself. He would have another plan i suppose.<br />Anyway we dont get told the number of shots Sartaj hears and he doesn't speak to Anjali about that operation so we just have to assume that Guruji died or was kept in secret custody by RAW<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
 <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
</span>
