<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1061720-this-book-came-up-as-a-recommendation">This book came up as a recommendation because I liked &quot;Shantaram&quot;. Are there any similarities other than the fact that it takes place in India? What I loved about Shantaram was the beautiful writing.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1061720'><a id="like_count_community_question_1061720" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/1061720?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">2 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F40090.Sacred_Games">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/1061720-this-book-came-up-as-a-recommendation">4 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/1061720-this-book-came-up-as-a-recommendation">See all 3 answers</a>
</li>
</ul>
